    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的忠犬被邪恶怪物掳走，是时候讨回公道了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203110/extras/3e2445027283e0a596c121484f2b5904.poster.avif?t=1767620205\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203110/extras/3e2445027283e0a596c121484f2b5904.webm?t=1767620205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203110/extras/3e2445027283e0a596c121484f2b5904.mp4?t=1767620205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Rogue Inferno》</strong>是一款基于方格的类Rogue卡组构筑游戏，策略与走位将决定胜负。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >方格战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一步都意义非凡。合理站位，在方格中闪避攻击、绕开敌人，并释放毁灭性的连招。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203110/extras/92afa44b06bd1dddbe3b0c49159381e7.avif?t=1767620205\" width=800 height=290 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >卡组构筑 × 战术博弈</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造属于你的专属牌组！在每回合中抽牌、出牌、管理手牌，用来进攻、防御，或打出致命连击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203110/extras/e946ee9096b65a95d29cc67bf0067fab.avif?t=1767620205\" width=800 height=290 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >数十种怪物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎战种类繁多的敌人，每个怪物都有独特的行为与战术。无论是分裂的史莱姆、爆炸型敌人，还是突变部族，每一次遭遇都将带来全新的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203110/extras/9745e3348d70037cb35acc75d54860e4.poster.avif?t=1767620205\" width=800 height=489 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203110/extras/9745e3348d70037cb35acc75d54860e4.webm?t=1767620205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有更多精彩内容等你探索！</p>",
